title: Old Man (disambiguation)
content:
Old Man may refer to:

NPCs[edit | edit source]

  • Old man, found on the deck of the wrecked ship north-west of Port Phasmatys
  • Old Man Ral, found near the entrance of Meiyerditch
  • Old Man Yarlo, a retired carpenter living in Varrock
  • Mysterious Old Man, a man who can teleport the player to the Maze and Mime Random events, or just hands out items
  • Wise Old Man, a legendary and very powerful Saradominist wizard and former adventurer, currently residing in Draynor Village
  • Strange Old Man, can be found digging in the Barrows mounds
  • Weird Old Man, an insane man outside the northern entrance to the Kalphite Lair
  • Odd Old Man can be found at his house in northern Silvarea, slightly north-east of Varrock and west of Paterdomus temple

Other[edit | edit source]

  • Old man (Discovery of the Runes)
